cards.title: Purchase travel insurance
cards.description:
Given that cancellation risk starts immediately (usually, but check your policy). 
So consider purchasing your travel insurance as you decide on your travel 
dates and ideally before you start to purchase.

Important
Purchase your travel insurance policy when you start to make your first 
purchase!

Always read the fine print - the Policy Disclosure Statement (PDS)!

todos.title: Consider cancel for any reason coverage (more expensive)
Airline or provider cancellation of service covered?
Financial default or bankruptcy of provider covered?
Disclosure what your insurer requires (e.g. pre-existing medical)

cards.title: Make a secure copy of your passport
cards.description:
Its useful to have a secure copy of your passport in can you lose it.
Leave them with family or store a copy (pdf with a password)in a cloud 
service.

cards.title: Purchase foreign currency
cards.description:
Consider purchasing some foreign currency prior to departure in case 
you have difficulty getting to an ATM on arrival.

cards.title: Airline check in
cards.description:
Always consider checking in online (where available) to select your seat early 
and potentially avoid longer queues at the airport for those who have not
checked in.
